- dashboard/src/dashboard/templates/index.html — add hx-timeout attribute to polling sections (e.g. 8s for a 10s poll interval)

Example error handler:
<script>
  document.addEventListener('htmx:responseError', function(evt) {
    evt.detail.target.innerHTML = '<div class="bg-red-900/30 border border-red-800 rounded-lg p-4 text-red-300 text-sm">Failed to load — retrying...</div>';
  });
</script>

This ensures a visual indicator appears on failure while HTMX continues to poll and will recover on the next successful response.

